{"word":"ἐκλογίζομαι","slug":"ἐκλογίζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐκλογίζομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> attic <el>-ιοῦμαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to compute, calculate</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to consider, reflect on</i>, <el>τι</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <el>περί τινος</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to reckon on</i>, <el>οὐδεὶς αὑτοῦ θάνατον ἐκλογίζεται</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}